    <item>
      <title>随着风险情绪反弹，亚洲股市上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/asian-stocks-to-climb-as-risk-sentiment-rebounds-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国消费者通胀预期的缓和，增强了美联储今年降息的理由，亚洲股市追随美国股市的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/asian-stocks-to-climb-as-risk-sentiment-rebounds-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 22:57:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度、印度尼西亚在老龄化世界的新兴市场投资者中脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-indonesia-standout-for-em-investors-in-aging-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富达国际和贝莱德投资研究所表示，随着人口结构开始在投资决策中发挥更大作用，印度和印度尼西亚等人口正在稳步增长的新兴市场必将受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-indonesia-standout-for-em-investors-in-aging-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
